{"tid":2095561,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"內蒙古確診一例鼠疫（黑死病），中國政府發布鼠疫三級警報","createTime":"2020-07-05T14:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T03:38:35.000Z","uid":48040,"like":242,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"249cc2a4ae9086ad8f739be1d2c37c520c1a15e9","tid":2095561,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"據《環球時報》最新消息指出，中國內蒙古自治區巴彥淖爾市於昨（4）日通報1例「腺鼠疫」疑似病例，衛健委經研究後，決定發布鼠疫防控3級預警，宣布自7月5日起進入預警期，並呼籲民眾嚴格遵守「3不3報」，包含不私自捕獵疫源動物、不剝食疫源動物、不私自攜帶疫源動物及其產品出疫區；發現病（死）旱獺及其他動物要報告、發現疑似鼠疫病人要報告、發現不明原因的高熱病人和急死病人要報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://med.china.com.cn/content/pid/189531/tid/1021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmed.china.com.cn%2Fcontent%2Fpid%2F189531%2Ftid%2F1021&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj32o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=7aeb8ce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://med.china.com.cn/content/pid/189531/tid/1021</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TyuR4gnpUqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTyuR4gnpUqs&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj32o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=32113e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TyuR4gnpUqs</a>"},{"pid":"85e6b9548fb7c06e18ceda5761be613813bb7743","tid":2095561,"uid":151313,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:22:23.000Z","msg":"可防可控"},{"pid":"d68d0d3518af6cca0a71219d740aa1fda87c3d54","tid":2095561,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0465b671f9ed8a0f736af84b222a5dc5f2c603e","tid":2095561,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"終於有新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0737af269bc98acef8b8bb0866b29b53f50a81e2","tid":2095561,"uid":48040,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"c0465b67